Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure III

data.description: Loan Assumption being offered by seller to qualified buyers!! Coastal Cottage! Over 1500 sqft of luxury just moments from the beach! Vacation home meets reality! Upon opening the front door you are met with a stunning entryway, footed with gorgeous wood flooring, overlooking the open floor plan. This beautiful home offers everything on your wish list! From the ultra high baseboards and plantation shutters to the pristine crown molding...no detail has been left untouched. Enveloped in natural sunlight, the spacious living room is centered by a classic fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings! Elegance meets functionality in this homes kitchen which features stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, tile backsplash, and an upgraded oversized single basin sink. With plenty of cabinet and countertop space, you'll also enjoy the practicality of the center island. For ultimate comfort and accommodation, escape to the Master Bedroom suite. With just the right amount of seclusion, the Master Bedroom features a spa like Master Bathroom offering a dual vanity, walk in shower, and a deep soaking tub. If you enjoy spending time outdoors, you will absolutely love the porch overlooking the tranquil backyard that offers an outdoor shower and your own garden. Even better, this home is solar powered!! This clean & elegant home is conveniently located half way between Jacksonville & Wilmington, in the sought-after subdivision, The Neighborhoods of Holly Ridge. This is your chance to own a piece of everyday vacation type life, where you're only moments from the beach and nestled in a neighborhood with sidewalks, streetlights, and a picnic area.
